overview: We specialize and have a high success rate in remediation of Depression/Mood Disorders, ADHD/ADD, Fibromyalgia, Cognitive Decline, Parkinson’s Disease, Chronic Fatigue Syndrome, Allergy (food, seasonal, environmental), Post Traumatic Stress Disorder (PTSD), Irritable Bowel Syndrome (IBS) and Anti-Aging Therapy. Those conditions have a strong connection to toxin, biotoxin and mercury exposure and are often misdiagnosed and mistreated.The Brain And Body Wellness Center is a private member association where the doctor- member relationship is a special partnership in which we treat all individuals with dignity and respect. Our goal is to make your experience with us first class in every aspect. Our team has been consistent in delivering exceptional care. Together, we will review your life and medical history, goals, and expectations. We will help you explore your options, advise you, and provide you with the highest quality of integrative medical care.
